In large saucepan over low heat, melt margarine. Add marshmallows; stir until melted and well blended. Remove from heat. (OR, in large microwaveable bowl, microwave margarine at HIGH 30-60 seconds to melt. Stir in marshmallows. Microwave at HIGH 1-12 minutes or until smooth when stirred, stirring after 45 seconds.) Stir in vanilla, raisins, apricots, almonds and seeds. Add cereals (lightly crush the KELLOGG'S CORN FLAKES* cereal), stirring until well coated. Using lightly-buttered spatula, press into buttered 2 L (9-inch) square pan. Cool. Cut into bars.